#. Tag: para
#: using-d-i.xml:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to know the whole truth about Software RAID, have a look at "
"<ulink url=\"&url-software-raid-howto;\">Software RAID HOWTO</ulink>."
msgstr ""
